>Description:
I'm using DrScheme v300 under MacOS X 10.4.3.
I'd understood that the DrScheme editor accepts
Emacs key bindings.  Apparently, though, they're
hard-wired in; I have changed some of my key
bindings on my system in the file
~/Library/KeyBindings/DefaultKeyBinding.dict .
They don't seem to be recognized in DrScheme,
though.  It would be nice if they were.

Thanks,

--DGK
